<Legal lang="en" path="/privacy" title="Privacy Notice" updated="July 1, 2026">
  <p>In compliance with Mexico's <strong>Federal Law on Protection of Personal Data Held by Private Parties (LFPDPPP)</strong> and applicable regulations, this Privacy Notice is made available to you.</p>

  <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
  <p><strong>Oscaromargp</strong> (operating under the brand <strong>PardeSantos</strong>), reachable at <a href="mailto:oscaromargp@gmail.com">oscaromargp@gmail.com</a> and phone <strong>6121077805</strong>, is responsible for the processing and protection of your personal data.</p>

  <h2>2. Data we collect</h2>
  <p>We collect, directly when you provide it through our forms: <strong>name, email, phone</strong>, information about your interest (project type, whether you own land), and the origin of your visit (campaign / UTM parameters). We do not collect sensitive personal data.</p>

  <h2>3. Purposes of processing</h2>
  <h3>Primary (necessary)</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>To contact you and handle your request for information and a quote.</li>
    <li>To prepare and send quotes and provide commercial follow-up.</li>
    <li>To manage your registration as a referral partner, where applicable.</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Secondary (optional)</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Sending news, promotions and content related to our products.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you do not want your data used for secondary purposes, you may say so by writing to our contact email; this will not be grounds to deny you the requested services.</p>

  <h2>4. Transfers</h2>
  <p>Your data may be processed by technology providers that supply us storage and automation services (e.g., database and workflow services), solely to fulfill the purposes described here and under confidentiality obligations. <strong>We do not sell your personal data.</strong> No transfers requiring your consent will occur without first obtaining it, except for the cases under Article 37 of the LFPDPPP.</p>

  <h2>5. ARCO rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to <strong>Access, Rectify, Cancel or Object</strong> to the processing of your data, and to withdraw consent. To exercise these rights, send your request to <a href="mailto:oscaromargp@gmail.com">oscaromargp@gmail.com</a> including your name, the data concerned, and proof of identity. We will respond within the legal timeframes.</p>

  <h2>6. Limiting use or disclosure</h2>
  <p>You may request, at any time, to limit the use or disclosure of your data via the contact email.</p>

  <h2>7. Tracking technologies</h2>
  <p>This site may use campaign parameters (UTM) and measurement technologies to understand visit origin and improve our communication. You can disable these from your browser settings.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes</h2>
  <p>Any change to this Privacy Notice will be published on this same page, showing the last update date.</p>
</Legal>
